subject: Sports Injuries
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Dog Sledding
lead_paragraph: Three veteran mushers — DeeDee Jonrowe, Lynwood Fielder and Jim Lanier — dropped out of the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race on Tuesday because of injuries on the treacherous trail.
